PractitionerIdentifierSearchParameter

Parameter practitioner.identifier:token

Searches for Practitioner by a given Practitioner eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Practitioner?identifier={identifier}

ResourcePractitioner
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesPractitioner
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
